                <h2 id="post-754">
                    <a href="http://joyridelabs.de/blog/?p=754" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Third Interview: Launchpad">
                        <span class="blogHeadline">Third Interview: Launchpad</span>
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <small>Wednesday, May 25th, 2011</small>

                <div>
                    <div class="en"><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="size-full wp-image-755 aligncenter" title="Nikki and the Launchpad" src="http://joyridelabs.de/blog//wp-content/uploads/2011/05/nikkiLP.png" alt="Nikki and the Launchpad" width="240" height="157" /></p>

<p>The open source project host Launchpad (we use their <a href="https://bugs.launchpad.net/nikki">bug tracker</a>) asked us a few questions which we answered in <a href="http://blog.launchpad.net/projects/nikki-and-the-robots">this little interview</a>.</p>

<p>Previews interviews (German): <a href="http://joyridelabs.de/blog/?p=404">Gameslabor</a> [<a href="http://translate.google.com/translate?js=n&amp;prev=_t&amp;hl=en&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;layout=2&amp;eotf=1&amp;sl=de&amp;tl=en&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fgameslabor.de%2Fdailyterror%2F1772-nikki-and-the-robots-entwickler-interview">English</a>], <a href="http://joyridelabs.de/blog/?p=344">Zockerperlen</a> [<a href="http://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en&amp;sl=de&amp;tl=en&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zockerperlen.de%2FJoyride-Laboratories-Die-Macher-von-Nikki-And-The-Robots-im-Gespraech-mit-Zockerperlen%2C20.html">English</a>].</p></div>
                </div>
